(Trying to get away with it)
%¥#%¥pig.

293
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:09,960
Why isn't it right?

294
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,120
#%#¥pig.

295
00:12:11,540 --> 00:12:12,340
(Wrong)

296
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:14,320
A pig that didn't cross the river.

297
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,280
Piggy hero.

298
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,340
(Just kidding)

299
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,480
River-crossing pig.

300
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:21,240
(Pig, river, block)
Pig didn't cross the river.

301
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,200
River-crossing pig.

302
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,080
River...

303
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:23,880
River pig.

304
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,520
Guinea pig.

305
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:26,860
(Guinea (river-blocked) pig)

306
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:28,990
(As expected of Ning)
I knew we could count on you.

307
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:31,200
Guinea pig.

308
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:31,760
That's right.

309
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,640
(Got three right, gets the seal)
You answered three riddles.

310
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:36,400
We are mortal enemies with pigs.

311
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,340
(We'll get it next time for sure)

312
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:38,680
I'll give you a stamp now.

313
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,120
Sure.

314
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,440
Let's go.

315
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:47,560
Let's go there.

316
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:48,840
I have Invisibility Card.

317
00:12:49,280 --> 00:12:50,920
What does it do again?

318
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,680
I can hide myself.

319
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:54,200
I can take all their stuff.

320
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:57,800
What's this?

321
00:12:57,800 --> 00:13:00,100
(Medicine)

322
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:00,840
What's this?

323
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,440
Medicine.

324
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,880
There's nothing here.

325
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:08,440
Don't miss out. Check us out!

326
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,720
(Fragrance wafts for miles)
Legendary stuffed bread.

327
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,640
(Each bite worthy of praise)
A single bite touches the soul.

328
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:16,080
Hello.

329
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:18,440
Smells amazing.

330
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,760
Did you make this?

331
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:20,120
Yes.

332
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:23,640
(Dong Jiaqi Tiffany as big eater vendor)
I brought this from Chang'an.

333
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:26,320
The famous one-bite stuffed bread.

334
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:30,840
If all of you can finish it in one bite,

335
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,560
you'll earn a stamp.

336
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,680
(Right up my alley)
That's too easy. Bring it on.

337
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,720
Look at this little foodie.

338
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:36,480
(Little foodie)
Little foodie

339
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,400
(Still growing)
is still growing)

340
00:13:37,460 --> 00:13:38,560
(Just you watch)

341
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,200
Okay.

342
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:40,360
Sit.

343
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,120
Let's sit here.

344
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,160
I think it's going to be delicious.

345
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,560
Ghost Market has everything.

346
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:45,600
(Ready to unleash the abyssal appetite)

347
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,320
Okay.

348
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,200
It should be really good.

349
00:13:48,220 --> 00:13:50,160
(Hungry and waiting)

350
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:51,000
Very delicious.

351
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,360
Not gonna lie.

352
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,320
It's pretty big.

353
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,280
It's a big bite.

354
00:13:57,660 --> 00:14:00,260
(Watch me swallow it whole)

355
00:14:00,300 --> 00:14:01,960
(Can't beat my appetite)

356
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,680
Is it good?

357
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,640
I'll try it too.

358
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:08,380
(Easy-peasy)

359
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,240
Is it good?

360
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:12,960
So simple.

361
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,780
(All in one bite)

362
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:18,740
(We got this)

363
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,020
(Mouth too small)

364
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:32,940
(Mouth can't cover the bread)

365
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:35,420
(A mouth full of food
leaves no room for mockery)

366
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:38,140
(Only one bread left
before they get the stamp)

367
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:42,700
(It's alright)

368
00:14:43,900 --> 00:14:46,180
(Won't give up)

369
00:14:55,420 --> 00:14:58,140
(Everyone succeeded)

370
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,240
This is awesome.

371
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,240
We're eating their food,

372
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,360
and they're giving us money.

373
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:03,040
(It's fun, we love it, come back often)

374
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,120
What kind of logic is this?

375
00:15:07,920 --> 00:15:08,960
Give me a napkin.

376
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:10,090
You ate it in one bite too?

377
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:14,960
It's delicious.

378
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,080
(Obtained two stamps)

379
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:17,960
Would you two like more stamps?

380
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:18,280
Of course.

381
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:18,760
Yes.

382
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:19,160
Okay.

383
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:21,800
Restore the Money-Saving Manual
in 30 seconds

384
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:23,360
to get one stamp.

385
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,240
Okay. We'll try.

386
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,320
Sure.

387
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,160
Find the corners first.

388
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:29,960
The bridge's here.

389
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:31,480
Here.

390
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:34,480
Done.

391
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,200
Isn't this Tongcheng Travel?

392
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,960
You know about this Money-Saving Manual?

393
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:40,560
Of course.

394
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:41,800
Tongcheng Travel app

395
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:43,440
makes booking stays very affordable.

396
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:45,840
We ought to travel the world
with Tongcheng Travel.

397
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,240
Yes. Not only is it cheap,

398
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,720
but you can also
get cash backs for bookings.

399
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:50,040
Save even more

400
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:51,320
with Tongcheng Travel.

401
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:55,720
Alright. I'll stamp your pass.

402
00:15:56,040 --> 00:15:57,040
Thank you.

403
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:58,520
You may continue your journey.

404
00:15:58,520 --> 00:15:58,800
Okay.

405
00:15:58,800 --> 00:15:59,480
Thank you.

406
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:01,640
At crucial moments, you can always
count on Tongcheng Travel.

407
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:03,440
Of course. Let's go.

408
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:06,480
Thank you.

409
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:08,840
It was delicious.

410
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:11,560
Come on.

411
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:13,000
Do a reading.

412
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:16,280
You ought to go a reading.

413
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,040
Come on.

414
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,140
Do a reading.

415
00:16:18,140 --> 00:16:19,740
(Yang Zhibo as fortune-telling vendor)

416
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:22,560
Esteemed guests,

417
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:25,720
I can tell you have many questions.

418
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,200
That's right.

419
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,800
One stamp grants you one question.

420
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:29,720
Okay.

421
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:31,360
You can ask anything.

422
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:32,520
Tonight,

423
00:16:32,520 --> 00:16:33,320
Who is the killer?

424
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,480
will it rain?

425
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:35,800
(A little humor)

426
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:36,160
Alright.

427
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,080
Tonight.

428
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:40,180
(Fortune teller accepted your request)
Tonight...

429
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:41,990
Wait. No!

430
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,460
(Argh!)

431
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,840
Think before you ask.

432
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,740
(I'll forgive you all)
Okay. We'll think about it.

433
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,200
Then let's ask him

434
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:55,850
who it is.

435
00:16:55,880 --> 00:16:56,840
(Ask him who brought Qide Sword)
Will he know?

436
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:59,520
I don't think we should ask that.

437
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,400
He won't tell us.

438
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:02,040
Okay.

439
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:03,920
Let's ask why didn't Ning Waver die.

440
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:04,110
Okay?

441
00:17:04,110 --> 00:17:04,680
Yeah. Sure.

442
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:04,960
Okay.

443
00:17:06,070 --> 00:17:07,110
One question.

444
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:07,830
Sure.

445
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,440
Why didn't...

446
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,640
You crossed it out
before I even asked you.

447
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:13,070
Why didn't Ning Waver die?

448
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:16,680
Have you forgotten

449
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:19,240
the legend
of the ghost soldier's resurrection?

450
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:24,520
Scammed me out of my money!

451
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:26,280
(Change it into a question)
So that's it?

452
00:17:26,280 --> 00:17:26,720
Yeah.

453
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,200
Yes.

454
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,520
Then he'll say you came back
because of the ghost soldiers.

455
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:29,520
I think we need another angle.

456
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:30,080
Another angle.

457
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:30,880
Where did

458
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:32,040
Yan Reason go?

459
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:32,680
What if he says,

460
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:34,320
"Don't you know"?

461
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:36,600
"Things have been really weird lately".

462
00:17:36,600 --> 00:17:37,480
Then we're done for again.

463
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:38,560
Then let's just beat him up, okay?

464
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:39,240
(Solving it by hand)
Okay, come on.

465
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:39,800
If he says that,

466
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,280
we'll beat him up.

467
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:40,960
Okay.

468
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:44,320
(The muscle is ready)
Where did Yan Reason go?

469
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:45,980
(Try talking nonsense again)

470
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:49,900
(I'm behaving now. Please spare me)

471
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:50,360
How about this?

472
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:53,040
Do you have anything

473
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,560
related to her?

474
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:56,100
You can describe it.

475
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:58,360
A pair of black embroidered shoes.

476
00:17:58,360 --> 00:17:59,920
(Yan)
They have beads and jade on them.

477
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,000
And a pattern.

478
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:03,200
There's a special pattern on the insole.

479
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:06,520
The mark
of the Thousand-Faced Eagle King.

480
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:07,760
Right. The Thousand-Faced Eagle King.

481
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:11,240
Ask him where else
that mark can be found.

482
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:14,240
(Where else is the Eagle King's mark?)
Where else is the Eagle King's mark?

483
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,040
The Thousand-Faced Eagle King

484
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:18,000
lives on top of this Black Tower.

485
00:18:27,020 --> 00:18:29,300
(Ghost Market. Black Tower)

486
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,440
But

487
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:32,320
there are two guards at the entrance.

488
00:18:32,320 --> 00:18:33,120
They're really tough.

489
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:33,760
Be careful.

490
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:41,480
Okay. How do we get in?

491
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:43,280
That will require

492
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:45,360
your wisdom and courage.

493
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:46,520
(One useless line for everyone)

494
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:48,800
I swear, I almost smacked you.

495
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:51,520
Seriously, what is wrong with you?

496
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,840
Where can we find the mystery man?

497
00:18:54,840 --> 00:18:55,840
On top of the Ghost Tower.

498
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:57,600
Does the mystery man

499
00:18:57,840 --> 00:18:59,320
have any specific look?

500
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:00,640
A black cloak.

501
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:02,840
He carries the Qide Sword.

502
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:04,160
The real Qide Sword.

503
00:19:04,800 --> 00:19:06,440
I just remembered something.

504
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:07,880
What?

505
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:12,440
Didn't I say I was selling Qide Swords?

506
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,440
And how did I get

507
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:14,880
those Qide Swords?

508
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,600
I didn't actually forge them.

509
00:19:17,120 --> 00:19:18,480
One day,

510
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:20,080
I was walking down the road,

511
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:20,960
and I found them.

512
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:22,200
Suddenly, I saw someone ahead.

513
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,720
He had a wine gourd.

514
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,960
He was a mystery man
who reeked of alcohol.

515
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:27,440
A wine gourd?

516
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:27,940
(A wine gourd again)

517
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:29,560
Didn't you make

518
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:30,480
a wine gourd for your master?

519
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,600
Yes. I made one for my master.

520
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,480
So his master...

521
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,160
(The one who sold He Ha the fake swords)
And my master also

522
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,440
(is Ding Pillar's master, Uncle Meng)
wears that black cloak.

523
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:37,640
Right.

524
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:38,600
And his hat...

525
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:40,240
I don't even know what he looks like.

526
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:40,760
Okay.

527
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:42,960
So it could be the same person.

528
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:44,040
Maybe he's the mystery man.

529
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:46,760
He's the one who gave me
fifty Qide Swords.

530
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:47,600
Fifty?

531
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:49,430
(Qide Sword wholesaler)
Fifty Qide Swords.

532
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,320
He told me to sell them.

533
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,080
Were those swords real?

534
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:52,880
They had to be fake.

535
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:53,360
Fake.

536
00:19:53,360 --> 00:19:54,680
I bought them cheap.

537
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,990
- Let's go in first.
- Let's go.

538
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:57,920
I'll go ask first.

539
00:20:02,320 --> 00:20:03,520
Let's just go.

540
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,640
What will happen if we go first?

541
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:05,880
Okay.

542
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,120
This is the Black Tower!

543
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:07,840
No outsiders allowed!

544
00:20:09,680 --> 00:20:10,920
Their eyes are so high up.

545
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,640
Can't we crawl in along the ground?

546
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,840
We're the Thousand-Faced
Eagle King's grandsons.

547
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,480
The Thousand-Faced Eagle King's
grandsons.

548
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,340
(Used to instantly
lowering their seniority)

549
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:20,240
Who said that?

550
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,360
You... Who wants to be his grandson?

551
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:22,920
(Don't drag us into this)
If you wanna be his grandson, go ahead.

552
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:25,320
We've got Skill Cards, right, guys?

553
00:20:25,320 --> 00:20:26,080
Invisibility Card.

554
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:27,160
Who has the Invisibility Card?

555
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:27,880
I have it.

556
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,680
(Ning Waver has the Invisibility Card)

557
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:29,880
I have the Transport Card.

558
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,320
Great. Then summon a train
and run them over.

559
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,800
Then we can get in.

560
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:36,020
(The idea guy is here)
Summon a plane.

561
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,000
Get a plane. We'll fly up there.

562
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,080
No. Just use a cannon.

563
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:40,840
Transport.

564
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:41,790
We'll ride the cannon later.

565
00:20:41,820 --> 00:20:43,080
(Who's the cannonball?)

566
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:44,200
I have the Disguise Card.

567
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,240
That's easy, then.

568
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,280
With the Disguise Card,

569
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:48,640
I'll just turn into them.

570
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,280
Exactly.

571
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:51,240
I can't walk on stilts, Ning.

572
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,080
No. Turn into
the Thousand-Faced Eagle King!

573
00:20:53,360 --> 00:20:53,800
I can't.

574
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:54,640
Because the Disguise Card

575
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:56,320
only works if you already know

576
00:20:56,320 --> 00:20:57,120
what they look like.

577
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:59,400
Then let's use the Invisibility Card.

578
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,120
The Invisibility Card.

579
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:02,200
Can we all turn invisible?

580
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:02,360
Yes.

581
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:03,800
Let's go invisible for three minutes.

582
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:05,120
No problem. Okay.

583
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:06,040
Come on.

584
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:06,400
Okay.

585
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,280
Three, two, one.

586
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:08,080
Use

587
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,350
the Invisibility Card!

588
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:13,540
(Invisibility Card: Hides you
from dungeon natives for 3 minutes)

589
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:18,120
Invisible cloak!

590
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:19,080
Okay. Let's go!

591
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:20,080
I can't see you guys!

592
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:20,800
Let's go!

593
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:21,760
Let me try.

594
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:25,920
Go. I'm good.

595
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,240
Go.

596
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,520
Why'd everyone disappear?

597
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:28,680
(Setting off)

598
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:29,720
Whose foot is this?

599
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,200
Lower.

600
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:31,920
There are no feet.

601
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:34,240
Whose arm is this?

602
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,240
Whose leg?

603
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:37,680
There are no feet.

604
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:40,120
Whose leg?

605
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:42,560
That's so weird.

606
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:44,460
(Easy pass)

607
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,280
Why are there so many legs?

608
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,160
(Can't get through?)
Go.

609
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:50,720
Get down!

610
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,440
Crouch.

611
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,440
Where's that leg from?

612
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:53,720
Crouch.

613
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,920
Crouch down, Ning.

614
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:56,920
Why is it gone?

615
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,200
It's gone.

616
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,400
Maybe we were seeing things.

617
00:21:59,420 --> 00:22:01,500
(Front-row spectators)

618
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:02,960
Go!

619
00:22:02,980 --> 00:22:04,140
(Sneaking along)

620
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:05,080
Hold on.

621
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:06,240
Your butts are in my face.

622
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,880
That's really rude.

623
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:11,240
Whose leg?

624
00:22:13,360 --> 00:22:14,160
Gone again.

625
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:17,060
Your butt is way too big.

626
00:22:17,060 --> 00:22:18,180
(Teammate roasting him)
Who bumped into me?

627
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:20,040
Wait.

628
00:22:20,040 --> 00:22:20,640
Who hit us?

629
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:22,440
Whose leg?

630
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:24,760
Close the door.

631
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:25,960
- Why's the door open?
- Close the door!

632
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:28,340
Is it that windy today?

633
00:22:31,580 --> 00:22:35,380
(Successfully entered the Black Tower)

634
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:36,320
See this symbol?

635
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:37,200
I see it.

636
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:37,840
Yeah, I see it.

637
00:22:37,840 --> 00:22:38,280
Eagle King.

638
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:43,940
(What does Yan Reason have to do
with the Thousand-Faced Eagle King?)

639
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:46,760
Who's crying?

640
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:50,780
(Where's that child crying coming from?)

641
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:53,240
Here!

642
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:55,040
Stairs.

643
00:22:56,660 --> 00:23:02,220
(Why is there a child crying
on the second floor?)

644
00:23:09,680 --> 00:23:11,080
It's okay. You're all safe now.

645
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,440
The healer said

646
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,880
that mysterious person in the cloak

647
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:15,320
gave you the antidote in time.

648
00:23:15,320 --> 00:23:16,520
So the poisoning wasn't too bad.

649
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:18,160
You just need rest to recover.

650
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:19,840
What does he mean, rest to recover?

651
00:23:20,120 --> 00:23:21,000
It should be

652
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,360
those kids with rotting wounds.

653
00:23:22,360 --> 00:23:23,760
The mysterious person
gave them medicine.

654
00:23:23,820 --> 00:23:25,980
(The mysterious person saved the kids)

655
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,480
So he's a good guy?

656
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:29,620
(Is the mysterious person good?)

657
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:31,560
(Second-floor guard post)
Did we save all the kids in the cells?

658
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:32,760
Except for the ones
who were already dead,

659
00:23:32,760 --> 00:23:33,680
we got them all out.

660
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:35,440
But Yan was taken by them.

661
00:23:36,360 --> 00:23:37,840
Yan?

662
00:23:38,180 --> 00:23:41,260
(Yan Reason was taken)

663
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:43,360
What? That Tui guy is awful!

664
00:23:43,360 --> 00:23:44,400
Exactly.

665
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:46,920
Back then, the Thousand-Faced
Eagle King made up

666
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:48,200
the ghost soldier legend

667
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:50,000
and built the Ghost Market
to scare off outsiders.

668
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:52,160
It was to protect
those important people,

669
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:54,640
and to give refugees like us,

670
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:55,680
poor folks like us,

671
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:57,280
a place to hide from the storm.

672
00:23:58,360 --> 00:23:59,600
But that Tui guy

673
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:01,600
used the ghost soldier story
to hurt children.

674
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:06,560
Used the ghost soldier story
to hurt children.

675
00:24:06,560 --> 00:24:08,920
So the Thousand-Faced Eagle King
is a good guy?

676
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:13,420
(Thousand-Faced Eagle King: created the
ghost soldier legend and Ghost Market)

677
00:24:13,420 --> 00:24:14,340
(To protect important people
and help refugees)

678
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:16,680
The Thousand-Faced Eagle King
was the one

679
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:19,000
who started this ghost soldier legend.

680
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:21,160
But his plan

681
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:23,200
was used by Lord Tui

682
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:24,440
to use this

683
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:25,360
to hurt children.

684
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:26,520
Right.

685
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,980
(Lord Tui used the "ghost soldier
legend" to persecute children)

686
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:29,840
Our Yan something...

687
00:24:29,840 --> 00:24:32,560
Yan Reason.

688
00:24:32,560 --> 00:24:33,840
Yan Reason was taken by them.

689
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:34,080
Now they're saying...

690
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:34,560
Right.

691
00:24:34,560 --> 00:24:36,840
She was taken while saving the children.

692
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:38,800
But who took her?

693
00:24:38,800 --> 00:24:41,120
Think about it. Lord Tui
is already dead.

694
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,120
So who could've taken

695
00:24:42,120 --> 00:24:42,760
Yan Reason?

696
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:45,380
(Who took Yan Reason
while she was saving the children?)

697
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:46,480
The Thousand-Faced Eagle King.

698
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:49,680
They said he's a good guy.

699
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:51,280
What if he wanted to save her?

700
00:24:51,280 --> 00:24:53,320
Didn't they say she was hurt? Missing?

701
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:54,400
She was bleeding. How could he save her?

702
00:24:55,320 --> 00:24:57,320
(Ning's guess: Yan is already dead)
Wait. I think someone's downstairs.

703
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,120
Let's check.

704
00:25:03,840 --> 00:25:04,720
Put this on.

705
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:05,800
Cover up.

706
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:06,320
Quick.

707
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,920
Someone's coming down.

708
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:12,200
No one's here?

709
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:14,040
That was probably the mechanism chair.

710
00:25:14,040 --> 00:25:15,480
Must be new intel again.

711
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:16,920
Mechanism chair?

712
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:18,000
New intel again?

713
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:20,720
This is the mechanism chair.

714
00:25:21,100 --> 00:25:25,940
(Mechanism chair)

715
00:25:38,080 --> 00:25:38,640
Two pieces of intel.

716
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:44,720
Intel one.

717
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:45,320
Let's read one first.

718
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:49,400
(Intel one)
The cloaked person holding

719
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:52,800
the real Qide Sword has been secretly
making fake swords to confuse everyone.

720
00:25:52,820 --> 00:25:55,300
(Someone has been secretly making
fake swords to confuse everyone)

721
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:56,040
We found out

722
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:58,760
he could enter and leave the Black Tower

723
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:01,680
(Intel one)
because he was very close

724
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:05,600
to Master Gui
who often treated the children there.

725
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:07,680
Intel two is

726
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:10,120
a photo of He Ha.

727
00:26:10,140 --> 00:26:11,960
(Intel two)

728
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,400
It's called Mastermind.

729
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:14,720
He says,

730
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:17,480
"That scammer selling Qide Swords
has entered the city".

731
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:19,000
"Should we kick him out"?

732
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:21,480
Then the reply says, "It's fine".

733
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:24,600
"No idiot would fall for his tricks".

734
00:26:24,600 --> 00:26:25,640
"Ignore him".

735
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:27,000
So one thing is confirmed.

736
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:29,640
The person who sold you the fake sword

737
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:30,200
is the mystery man.

738
00:26:30,260 --> 00:26:32,780
(Guess: the person who sold He Ha
the fake sword is the mystery man)

739
00:26:32,800 --> 00:26:33,880
The guy who sold you the fake sword

740
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,880
must have the real one, right?

741
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:37,920
And your key clue was that...

742
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:38,880
He wore a black cloak.

743
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,760
His hood covered his face,

744
00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:42,000
and he had a jade pendant
with "Xia" on it.

745
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,560
I couldn't see his face.

746
00:26:44,080 --> 00:26:45,840
Every night, he came to teach me.

747
00:26:45,840 --> 00:26:46,800
At dawn, he left.

748
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:48,360
Okay. Then it's possible that

749
00:26:48,360 --> 00:26:49,120
his teacher and the person

750
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:50,200
(Ding Pillar's teacher)
who sold you the fake sword

751
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,320
(The person who sold He the fake sword)
are the same person.

752
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:53,540
(Same person)

753
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:54,440
But

754
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,800
why would he sell fake Qide Swords?

755
00:26:57,800 --> 00:26:59,080
To protect the real sword.

756
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:00,640
Right. To confuse everyone.

757
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:03,720
And he's really close to that master.

758
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:06,160
(He was close to Master Gui)
He used the medicine to save the kids.

759
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,800
There was a healer stall.

760
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:08,760
Did it sell medicine?

761
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:10,680
Yes, but no one was there.

762
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:13,040
There's nothing here.

763
00:27:14,280 --> 00:27:16,560
Can we find Master Gui there

764
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:17,760
and ask him about
the Thousand-Faced Eagle King?

765
00:27:17,760 --> 00:27:19,160
Exactly. Let's go.

766
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:20,120
So what if we walk out
like we own the place?

767
00:27:20,120 --> 00:27:20,760
They won't let us in.

768
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:21,720
They can't stop us from leaving, right?

769
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,000
Makes sense.

770
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,080
Move aside, guys.

771
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:26,200
Three, two, one.

772
00:27:27,740 --> 00:27:28,660
(Walking out like bosses)

773
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:29,760
Hold on. Who let you in?

774
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:31,440
Go!

775
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:32,720
Move it!

776
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:35,000
Where did all these people come from?

777
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,200
Getting in is hard.

778
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,040
Getting out is easy.

779
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:38,720
Get out!

780
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,600
Go!

781
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:40,000
Okay.

782
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:40,800
Hurry!

783
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:41,680
Okay.

784
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:42,400
Who let you in?

785
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:44,640
- Okay.
- Hurry!

786
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:46,360
=The Truth (Season 4)=
Okay. Let's go find Master Gui.

787
00:27:46,360 --> 00:27:47,900
(Loading)

788
00:27:48,020 --> 00:27:50,540
(Medicine)

789
00:28:02,820 --> 00:28:05,380
(Master Gui, played by Lin Tan)

790
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,200
There really is someone here.

791
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:06,920
Come on, guys.

792
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:07,600
Someone's here.

793
00:28:07,600 --> 00:28:08,440
Hello.

794
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:10,800
Master.

795
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:12,040
Come. Have a seat.

796
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:15,200
Come on, Ning.

797
00:28:16,520 --> 00:28:17,000
Master.

798
00:28:17,320 --> 00:28:19,160
Come. I'll check your pulse first.

799
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,160
Another pulse check?

800
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:24,640
Go ahead.

801
00:28:25,020 --> 00:28:26,900
(We're already here)

802
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,400
This is a woman's pulse.

803
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:31,240
So you can't see, right?

804
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,360
I have a slight eye condition.

805
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:36,260
(Master Gui has an eye condition)

806
00:28:36,280 --> 00:28:36,880
Not bad.

807
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:38,760
Judging by your pulse,

808
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:41,480
this is classic career brain
with a foodie soul.

809
00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:43,160
(Diagnosed with career brain
+ foodie soul)

810
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:46,240
Your pulse has a clever spark
of everyday life.

811
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:49,960
Three parts street smarts,
seven parts brilliance.

812
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:50,920
I believe

813
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:51,520
standing before me

814
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:53,480
must be a steel-boned beauty.

815
00:28:54,320 --> 00:28:55,480
Steel-boned?

816
00:28:57,420 --> 00:28:58,620
(Bang bang or not bang bang)
A steel beauty.

817
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:00,200
You're good at compliments.

818
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:00,520
My turn.

819
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:01,920
Here.

820
00:29:02,600 --> 00:29:03,240
Come on. Praise me.

821
00:29:03,260 --> 00:29:06,100
(Waiting for praise)

822
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:08,560
Sir,

823
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:10,920
you should pay more attention

824
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:12,120
to your heart lately.

825
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,440
For real?

826
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,480
Based on my reading,

827
00:29:18,480 --> 00:29:19,720
in July,

828
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:22,600
you'll meet a woman
who makes your heart race.

829
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:23,800
One look at her,

830
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:25,880
and you'll feel like you're burning up.

831
00:29:30,340 --> 00:29:32,020
(He got all that from a pulse?)

832
00:29:32,040 --> 00:29:33,760
Burning up that much?

833
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:36,120
Isn't that a little too hot?

834
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:37,000
Too accurate.

835
00:29:37,420 --> 00:29:39,060
(Stay tuned for Overdo)

836
00:29:39,080 --> 00:29:40,560
One moment, she says she loves you.

837
00:29:40,560 --> 00:29:42,120
The next, she says she hates you.

838
00:29:42,120 --> 00:29:44,040
Then she pretends she doesn't love you.

839
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,400
Then she loves you like crazy.

840
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,600
In short, sir,

841
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:50,280
your heart is in for a wild ride.

842
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,000
Master,

843
00:29:52,280 --> 00:29:52,720
so

844
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:54,520
how do I survive this?

845
00:29:54,520 --> 00:29:55,600
It's not something to survive.

846
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:56,440
Just let it happen.

847
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,560
(Just let him burn)
No cure.

848
00:29:58,560 --> 00:30:01,240
You're destined to burn!

849
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:03,320
That was a great pulse reading.

850
00:30:03,320 --> 00:30:05,360
I love watching He fall in love.

851
00:30:05,360 --> 00:30:06,640
Master, I'm sick too.

852
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,680
I always think people like me.
What should I do?

853
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:09,480
Okay.

854
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:10,600
Let me take a good look.

855
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:14,040
This is clearly a happy pulse.

856
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:16,280
Not again.

857
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:17,440
Here we go again.

858
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:18,560
Not that kind of happy.

859
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:19,960
The happiness I mean

860
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,160
is joy.

861
00:30:22,080 --> 00:30:24,000
In other words,

862
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,480
(Beaming with joy)
you're really good

863
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,840
at lifting the mood around you.

864
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:29,320
It's joy as in charming.

865
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:30,360
Nice.

866
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:33,840
Okay. Come on, Master.

867
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:35,000
You...

868
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:35,800
(Check me too)

869
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:36,360
Seriously.

870
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:37,040
Master Gui.

871
00:30:37,600 --> 00:30:38,200
Very creepy.

872
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:41,680
Wait.

873
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:42,720
What?

874
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:43,800
Why can't I feel your pulse?

875
00:30:44,300 --> 00:30:46,180
(Why does Ning Waver have no pulse?)

876
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:50,240
What?

877
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:52,400
Could you be a dead man?

878
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:54,680
That's strange.

879
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:57,880
How can a dead man walk

880
00:30:57,880 --> 00:31:00,240
and talk like he's alive?

881
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,760
We can even see him.

882
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:02,440
Right.

883
00:31:02,840 --> 00:31:04,480
Life and death are major illnesses.

884
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,680
This man has a serious condition.

885
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,360
Look at my little clinic.

886
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,480
It's so simple.

887
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:12,280
You should find another way.

888
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:13,120
I can't treat this.

889
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:14,520
Then I want to ask.

890
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:16,920
What's this about you

891
00:31:16,920 --> 00:31:17,800
saving children?

892
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:18,400
Children?

893
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:18,880
Yes.

894
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:23,160
A mysterious person
holding the Qide Sword

895
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,840
often used your connection

896
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:26,560
to enter that tower

897
00:31:26,560 --> 00:31:27,600
and treat the children.

898
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,680
Who is that person?

899
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:34,240
You're talking about
a very mysterious person, right?

900
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:34,520
Yes.

901
00:31:34,520 --> 00:31:35,040
Very mysterious.

902
00:31:35,520 --> 00:31:36,520
A mysterious person.

903
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:37,680
That mysterious person

904
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:40,440
has been coming here a lot
lately for medicine.

905
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:43,860
(The mysterious person has been
getting medicine here lately)

906
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,960
But a gentleman's friendship
is light as water.

907
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,680
I don't know his name.

908
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:48,800
Also,

909
00:31:48,800 --> 00:31:50,600
I have some trouble with my eyes.

910
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:52,800
So I never saw what
he really looked like.

911
00:31:52,940 --> 00:31:54,880
(Master Gui doesn't know who he is)
I just remember

912
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,640
he often wore

913
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,880
a cloak.

914
00:31:59,040 --> 00:32:00,840
A few weeks ago, the last time

915
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:02,120
he came here for medicine,

916
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:03,440
he was badly poisoned.

917
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,680
The poison had reached his bones.

918
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:06,360
So I checked his pulse.

919
00:32:06,360 --> 00:32:07,880
I found that his time was almost up.

920
00:32:07,880 --> 00:32:10,120
He didn't have much longer.

921
00:32:10,560 --> 00:32:11,320
So I asked him,

922
00:32:11,320 --> 00:32:12,080
with poison this severe,

923
00:32:12,080 --> 00:32:14,470
(The mystery man was poisoned and dying)
how did you get poisoned?

924
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:15,200
He said

925
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:17,040
it was because of those children.

926
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,520
To save them, he tested the medicine

927
00:32:19,520 --> 00:32:20,800
on himself.

928
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:24,220
(The mysterious person risked himself
to save the children)

929
00:32:24,760 --> 00:32:26,600
Those children ate the rotten soup

930
00:32:26,600 --> 00:32:27,440
and were poisoned.

931
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:29,040
He couldn't find the cure,

932
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:30,320
so he had no choice

933
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:31,920
but to use himself as a test subject.

934
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:33,240
He tried each medicine one by one.

935
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,560
Then I asked him,

936
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,880
why go that far?

937
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:39,720
He said those children
are Tui Kingdom's future.

938
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:41,720
As long as he could heal them,

939
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:44,000
even giving up his own life

940
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:45,040
would be worth it.

941
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:48,440
He even joked with me.

942
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:51,120
He said the medicine
was so hard to swallow.

943
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:53,400
If only it tasted

944
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:56,160
as good as his usual
god-tier stuffed bread,

945
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,200
he'd still gladly do it.

946
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:03,580
(The highest chivalry is sacrificing
oneself for what is right)

947
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:04,880
Right.

948
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:06,160
He also left

949
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:07,480
this wooden box with me.

950
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:10,440
I never opened it.

951
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:13,080
I don't know what's inside either.

952
00:33:13,080 --> 00:33:13,520
Everyone,

953
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:14,640
I think

954
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:15,480
you're good people.

955
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:16,920
He's a good person too.

956
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,040
So this box

957
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,600
is now in your care.

958
00:33:19,600 --> 00:33:20,440
Okay.

959
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:22,240
It's Da Men Junzi.

960
00:33:22,980 --> 00:33:25,580
(It's Da Men Junzi)

961
00:33:31,840 --> 00:33:32,660
A wine flask.

962
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:33,880
Meng.

963
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:34,840
Master Meng.

964
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:36,480
This belongs to my master.

965
00:33:37,120 --> 00:33:39,280
(Meng, wine flask)
My master, Uncle Meng.

966
00:33:39,320 --> 00:33:40,280
His wine flask broke,

967
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:41,880
so I made him a new one

968
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:42,600
and engraved the character Meng on it.

969
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:43,920
My master.

970
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:45,240
(Uncle Meng is the mysterious person)

971
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:47,240
This is my tonic, right?

972
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:49,520
You've taken this medicine?

973
00:33:49,520 --> 00:33:50,800
After I fell off the cliff,

974
00:33:50,800 --> 00:33:52,080
Junzi Ruyu

975
00:33:52,080 --> 00:33:54,240
would always bring me special tonics

976
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:55,320
to help me recover.

977
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:56,400
Special tonic

978
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,680
restores inner strength.

979
00:33:57,680 --> 00:34:00,680
Specifically cures the effects
of Eleven-Spice Tendon Powder.

980
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:02,040
Not long after taking it,

981
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:03,400
my inner strength returned.

982
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,460
(Ke Stubborn's antidote was given
by the mysterious person.)

983
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,040
Whose clothes are these?

984
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,160
These are mine.

985
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:09,280
Your clothes?

986
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:12,120
That day, I followed the man in black,

987
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:12,960
then

988
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:13,960
I almost got discovered.

989
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:14,320
Then...

990
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:15,150
Someone rescued you.

991
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:17,000
He grabbed my collar and pulled me away.

992
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:18,360
(The mysterious person saved Yang Glory)
So

993
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,190
a piece of the clothing was torn off.

994
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:20,710
There's a receipt here.

995
00:34:20,710 --> 00:34:21,320
(Tui City Money House Receipt)

996
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,440
All debts are settled.

997
00:34:22,440 --> 00:34:24,360
The principal and interest
owed by Jin Thrifty

998
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:26,400
have been fully repaid.

999
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:28,190
From this day onward,

1000
00:34:28,190 --> 00:34:30,400
we will no longer trouble her.

1001
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:31,670
This is hereby certified.

1002
00:34:31,670 --> 00:34:32,760
Tui City Money House.

1003
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:34,960
Yes, I borrowed money
from this money house.

1004
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:36,150
Why is the receipt in this box?

1005
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:37,520
It means this person

1006
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:39,150
is connected to all of us.

1007
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,920
He has secretly been helping everyone.

1008
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:41,670
He repaid your debt.

1009
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:44,840
So this so-called Uncle Meng,
the mysterious person,

1010
00:34:44,840 --> 00:34:46,960
has helped all four of you before,
right?

1011
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:47,520
Yes.

1012
00:34:47,540 --> 00:34:50,140
(The mysterious person, Uncle Meng,
taught Ding Pillar martial arts)

1013
00:34:50,180 --> 00:34:52,540
(The mysterious person
repaid Jin Thrifty's debt)

1014
00:34:52,580 --> 00:34:55,140
(The mysterious person gave
Ke Stubborn the antidote)

1015
00:34:55,220 --> 00:34:57,740
(The mysterious person
rescued Yang Glory in a crisis)

1016
00:34:57,820 --> 00:35:02,300
(Why did the mysterious
person secretly help everyone?)

1017
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:03,360
Right, everyone.

1018
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:05,240
I just remembered.

1019
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,600
He left

1020
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:08,200
a package with me.

1021
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:12,920
What is this?

1022
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:17,120
What is this rod?

1023
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:18,360
Bamboo?

1024
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:18,960
Distance.

1025
00:35:21,460 --> 00:35:23,500
(Distance)

1026
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:24,840
Four Symbols Manual.

1027
00:35:25,600 --> 00:35:26,600
Four Symbols Manual.

1028
00:35:26,600 --> 00:35:29,480
There are four hidden martial arts
skills in the martial world.

1029
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:31,240
They require strong inner power to use.

1030
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:33,920
But if all four skills
are used together,

1031
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:36,480
the user will be immobilized
for fifteen breaths.

1032
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,160
What does that mean?

1033
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:38,400
You will be frozen in place
for fifteen breaths.

1034
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:39,700
(Black pink)

1035
00:35:40,080 --> 00:35:41,320
You will stop for fifteen breaths.

1036
00:35:41,680 --> 00:35:43,360
The four skills are extremely powerful.

1037
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:45,560
Only specific moves can counter them.

1038
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:48,760
However, the four counter
moves restrain each other.

1039
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:51,720
If all four are used at the same time,

1040
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:52,920
the user will suffer backlash.

1041
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,280
One of the four secret skills

1042
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:57,720
is Hedong Roar.

1043
00:35:58,080 --> 00:35:59,800
Countered only
by Cosmic Absorbing Skill.

1044
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:01,200
The second secret skill

1045
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,440
is Dark Rope Skill.

1046
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:04,320
Countered only by Toad Skill.

1047
00:36:04,320 --> 00:36:05,840
The third secret skill

1048
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:06,840
is Itch Finger.

1049
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:09,480
Countered only
by Enjoying the Claim the Gain.

1050
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:11,000
The fourth secret skill

1051
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:12,280
is Sandstrike.

1052
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:14,720
Countered only by Groundquake Skill.

1053
00:36:15,560 --> 00:36:18,120
The order of the four counter moves

1054
00:36:18,120 --> 00:36:20,160
will result in different
backlash symptoms.

1055
00:36:20,730 --> 00:36:22,240
(Blindness)

1056
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:22,950
(Frantic Dancing)

1057
00:36:22,950 --> 00:36:24,100
(Spinning Around)

1058
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:25,560
(Lost All Inner Power)

1059
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:26,340
(Paralyzed)

1060
00:36:26,340 --> 00:36:26,860
(Handstand)

1061
00:36:26,860 --> 00:36:29,540
(Different counterattack orders
result in different backlash effects)

1062
00:36:37,580 --> 00:36:40,780
(Cosmic Absorbing Mark)

1063
00:36:42,060 --> 00:36:44,620
(Frog Palm Mark)

1064
00:36:44,740 --> 00:36:47,420
(Butt Mark)

1065
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:49,220
(Shattered by Ground Shake)

1066
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,960
Could it be

1067
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:54,040
the marks on the mountain manor?

1068
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:57,000
Probably.

1069
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:57,800
Maybe.

1070
00:36:58,120 --> 00:37:00,480
Your father used three moves,
and you also used three moves.

1071
00:37:00,480 --> 00:37:02,680
These three moves left traces behind.

1072
00:37:02,680 --> 00:37:03,920
Shouldn't there be three people?

1073
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,280
There are three people.

1074
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:09,840
One culprit, a father and son.

1075
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:11,540
(Lord Tui, Ning Waver & mysterious guy)
Yes.

1076
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:13,240
The one holding the Qide Sword
was the culprit.

1077
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:13,800
The Qide Sword.

1078
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:14,520
The mysterious person

1079
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,400
exchanged moves with it.

1080
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,240
And this was left behind
by the culprit, right?

1081
00:37:17,260 --> 00:37:19,500
(Ding Pillar's theory: The Four Symbols
Manual was the culprit's)

1082
00:37:19,520 --> 00:37:22,040
Then where was he
while the fight happened?

1083
00:37:22,040 --> 00:37:22,900
(Where was Ning Waver at that time?)
He was already...

1084
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:25,000
Lying there.

1085
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:25,800
He was lying there.

1086
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:28,320
Then the mysterious person
and Lord Tui fought there.

1087
00:37:28,720 --> 00:37:29,360
That's right.

1088
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:32,420
(Ding Pillar's theory: Culprit fought
Lord Tui, Ning Waver was out.)

1089
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:33,280
I think it happened like this.

1090
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:36,040
The mysterious guy brought
the Qide Sword to kill his father.

1091
00:37:36,040 --> 00:37:37,520
His father used
the Cosmic Absorbing Skill

1092
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:39,000
to pull his son over

1093
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:40,240
and use him as a shield.

1094
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:41,780
(The sacrifice)

1095
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:43,480
Unexpectedly, the sword

1096
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,520
pierced through both of them.

1097
00:37:45,540 --> 00:37:47,620
(Jin Thrifty's theory: Lord Tui
used Ning Waver to block the sword.)

1098
00:37:47,620 --> 00:37:49,020
(Both were pierced
by the culprit's sword)

1099
00:37:49,040 --> 00:37:50,480
The Toad Skill definitely exists, right?

1100
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:51,120
Yes.

1101
00:37:51,120 --> 00:37:51,560
They all exist.

1102
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:53,240
He just doesn't know the order.

1103
00:37:53,240 --> 00:37:53,720
That's right.

1104
00:38:00,420 --> 00:38:01,780
(Who fought whom?)

1105
00:38:01,780 --> 00:38:03,240
(Crime scene clues?)
Let's head back.

1106
00:38:03,240 --> 00:38:04,520
I'll use the Transport Card

1107
00:38:04,520 --> 00:38:05,400
to take us back, okay?

1108
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:05,760
Okay.

1109
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:09,360
Using Transport Card.

1110
00:38:09,700 --> 00:38:10,980
(Transport Card: Obtain a vehicle.)

1111
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:14,780
(Transport Card)

1112
00:38:19,640 --> 00:38:21,120
Could it be the Portal Door?

1113
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:22,680
Is this real?

1114
00:38:23,160 --> 00:38:24,560
Is this our vehicle?

1115
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,000
What is this?

1116
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,280
The Portal Door.

1117
00:38:27,080 --> 00:38:28,200
Let's go.

1118
00:38:32,080 --> 00:38:32,760
We're really here.

1119
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:33,240
We're back.

1120
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:35,880
We got back instantly.

1121
00:38:37,640 --> 00:38:38,800
Everything is clear now.

1122
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:39,360
This...

1123
00:38:43,520 --> 00:38:45,040
this is the last position of the move.

1124
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:46,200
Yes.

1125
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:49,770
(The final skill before death)
The pull ended here.

1126
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:50,800
I think we can

1127
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,880
use the victim's position

1128
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:52,600
to reconstruct what happened.

1129
00:38:52,860 --> 00:38:53,380
(He Ha's theory:
