01:25:27,880 --> 01:25:28,640
Who'd you vote for?

2758
01:25:28,640 --> 01:25:29,840
I voted for him.

2759
01:25:29,840 --> 01:25:30,360
You?

2760
01:25:30,920 --> 01:25:31,480
Him.

2761
01:25:32,260 --> 01:25:34,180
(Missed the Golden Key)

2762
01:25:40,440 --> 01:25:41,000
Don't jump!

2763
01:25:44,840 --> 01:25:47,920
Actually, when we were leaving,

2764
01:25:47,920 --> 01:25:49,480
he suddenly patted me.

2765
01:25:49,480 --> 01:25:50,560
Then he looked at my clothes.

2766
01:25:50,560 --> 01:25:51,760
When we were leaving?

2767
01:25:51,760 --> 01:25:53,040
Leaving where? From where?

2768
01:25:53,040 --> 01:25:54,320
Before we went to the Ghost Market.

2769
01:26:00,760 --> 01:26:01,320
Good thing you took it off.

2770
01:26:01,580 --> 01:26:02,900
(So random)
What the heck?

2771
01:26:03,240 --> 01:26:04,760
I didn't get it at the time.

2772
01:26:05,200 --> 01:26:06,800
But after I saw that receipt...

2773
01:26:06,800 --> 01:26:07,560
(Receipt)

2774
01:26:07,560 --> 01:26:09,040
(Bought two black robes)
I got it.

2775
01:26:09,500 --> 01:26:11,060
(To hide the silver mark left
by Qide Sword's stab)

2776
01:26:11,060 --> 01:26:12,620
(He needed two identical robes
to change into)

2777
01:26:14,080 --> 01:26:15,200
Weren't you watching him?

2778
01:26:16,400 --> 01:26:17,600
I didn't watch him closely.

2779
01:26:17,600 --> 01:26:18,960
I was watching him the whole time.

2780
01:26:18,960 --> 01:26:19,960
I don't know why.

2781
01:26:19,980 --> 01:26:22,020
(The charm of deduction)

2782
01:26:22,200 --> 01:26:23,720
I really did lose my memory, guys.

2783
01:26:23,720 --> 01:26:25,120
I know.

2784
01:26:25,880 --> 01:26:27,400
All I can say is...

2785
01:26:29,460 --> 01:26:31,780
(I admit defeat)

2786
01:26:32,080 --> 01:26:33,280
(Humble)
No, you let me win.

2787
01:26:33,280 --> 01:26:34,520
You let me win.

2788
01:26:34,960 --> 01:26:36,800
You've been something else this season.

2789
01:26:37,720 --> 01:26:38,320
I'm telling you.

2790
01:26:38,320 --> 01:26:39,720
Right now, I just wanna ask.

2791
01:26:39,720 --> 01:26:41,880
How many Golden Keys
does Liu Yuning have?

2792
01:26:42,520 --> 01:26:43,040
Yeah.

2793
01:26:43,040 --> 01:26:43,920
Right now, I think...

2794
01:26:43,920 --> 01:26:45,400
Looks like he's first now.

2795
01:26:45,580 --> 01:26:46,840
(Player Liu Yuning: Gold Keys x4)

2796
01:26:46,840 --> 01:26:48,040
I could've...

2797
01:26:48,180 --> 01:26:50,340
(Player TNT Ding Chengxin: Gold Keys x3)

2798
01:26:50,360 --> 01:26:52,000
Honestly, I wanted to help
the good guys win today.

2799
01:26:52,000 --> 01:26:53,680
Then why didn't you?

2800
01:26:54,100 --> 01:26:55,540
(My Golden Keys)

2801
01:26:55,760 --> 01:26:57,120
Need a comeback, honestly.

2802
01:26:57,120 --> 01:26:58,640
I don't even wanna scold
you anymore. Seriously.

2803
01:27:00,120 --> 01:27:01,200
From my point of view,

2804
01:27:01,200 --> 01:27:03,160
I had to choose one of three.
How could I choose?

2805
01:27:03,160 --> 01:27:04,380
(This is too hard)

2806
01:27:05,360 --> 01:27:06,560
Listen to the key evidence.

2807
01:27:06,560 --> 01:27:07,160
It's really interesting.

2808
01:27:07,160 --> 01:27:08,480
I know where this was.

2809
01:27:11,040 --> 01:27:12,280
We were so close.

2810
01:27:12,280 --> 01:27:13,080
What?

2811
01:27:13,080 --> 01:27:14,640
The key evidence we missed in this case.

2812
01:27:15,040 --> 01:27:18,040
There were silver marks
and bloodstains inside the sword case.

2813
01:27:18,040 --> 01:27:19,060
(Ke Stubborn's sword case
had silver marks and bloodstains)

2814
01:27:19,360 --> 01:27:19,800
Sword case?

2815
01:27:21,160 --> 01:27:21,920
I kept playing with it.

2816
01:27:22,600 --> 01:27:24,520
It proves he put the real Qide Sword

2817
01:27:24,520 --> 01:27:25,960
inside his own sword case.

2818
01:27:25,960 --> 01:27:26,860
(The sheath had silver marks
and bloodstains)

2819
01:27:32,420 --> 01:27:33,940
(My head hurts)

2820
01:27:34,720 --> 01:27:35,400
Didn't see that coming, huh?

2821
01:27:39,720 --> 01:27:40,680
But I remember.

2822
01:27:40,680 --> 01:27:42,600
I remember someone asked about it.

2823
01:27:43,120 --> 01:27:43,480
Him.

2824
01:27:43,480 --> 01:27:44,440
I was there.

2825
01:27:44,440 --> 01:27:45,280
I went there to play with it.

2826
01:27:45,280 --> 01:27:46,600
He told me to stop.

2827
01:27:46,600 --> 01:27:48,360
I played with every sword there.

2828
01:27:48,360 --> 01:27:50,360
I just wanted to see
if he had that thing.

2829
01:27:50,360 --> 01:27:50,840
Right.

2830
01:27:54,800 --> 01:27:55,720
Stop messing with my swords.

2831
01:27:55,720 --> 01:27:57,880
I wanted to see
if the Qide Sword was inside.

2832
01:27:57,880 --> 01:27:58,920
There isn't the Qide Sword.

2833
01:27:58,920 --> 01:28:01,360
You were this close!

2834
01:28:01,920 --> 01:28:04,200
(Another billion-point emotional hit)
You were this close!

2835
01:28:04,560 --> 01:28:05,000
This close.

2836
01:28:08,000 --> 01:28:09,120
It slipped right past us.

2837
01:28:09,120 --> 01:28:09,840
Babe.

2838
01:28:09,860 --> 01:28:10,860
(Babe)

2839
01:28:10,860 --> 01:28:12,340
(Don't cry)

2840
01:28:13,040 --> 01:28:13,520
Nothing we can do.

2841
01:28:14,960 --> 01:28:16,120
A narrow loss.

2842
01:28:17,020 --> 01:28:18,700
(A narrow loss)

2843
01:28:19,040 --> 01:28:20,800
Let's sum up
the suspicious points, guys.

2844
01:28:20,800 --> 01:28:22,000
First.

2845
01:28:22,000 --> 01:28:24,800
How did I come back to life?

2846
01:28:24,800 --> 01:28:25,400
Exactly.

2847
01:28:25,400 --> 01:28:26,640
Why didn't you have a pulse?

2848
01:28:26,740 --> 01:28:30,460
(Why did Ning Waver come back to life?)

2849
01:28:30,520 --> 01:28:32,200
Did you all forget

2850
01:28:32,200 --> 01:28:35,040
the legend of the ghost soldiers
coming back to life?

2851
01:28:35,960 --> 01:28:36,280
No.

2852
01:28:36,280 --> 01:28:38,960
The fortune-teller said it.

2853
01:28:38,960 --> 01:28:40,440
He said your revival

2854
01:28:40,440 --> 01:28:43,360
might be connected
to the ghost soldier legend.

2855
01:28:43,460 --> 01:28:45,180
(Ning's revival may be connected
to the ghost soldier legend)

2856
01:28:45,560 --> 01:28:46,440
Right. Ghost soldiers revive.

2857
01:28:46,440 --> 01:28:47,040
That's possible.

2858
01:28:47,040 --> 01:28:47,680
Right.

2859
01:28:48,360 --> 01:28:49,640
So you're a real ghost soldier.

2860
01:28:50,600 --> 01:28:51,520
Stop it.

2861
01:28:55,480 --> 01:28:56,960
Is this some Lam Ching-ying thing?

2862
01:29:02,800 --> 01:29:04,460
(Emergency brake)
That got way too spooky.

2863
01:29:04,480 --> 01:29:05,640
Wasn't that fake?

2864
01:29:05,640 --> 01:29:07,680
Where did this legend even come from?

2865
01:29:07,680 --> 01:29:09,880
And how did those people lose back then?

2866
01:29:09,880 --> 01:29:11,640
Wait. Wasn't it
the Thousand-Faced Eagle King?

2867
01:29:11,640 --> 01:29:14,160
Didn't the Thousand-Faced
Eagle King start that rumor?

2868
01:29:14,440 --> 01:29:15,720
We still don't know who the

2869
01:29:15,720 --> 01:29:16,560
Thousand-Faced Eagle King is.

2870
01:29:16,560 --> 01:29:16,920
Right.

2871
01:29:17,300 --> 01:29:19,220
(Who could the Thousand-Faced
Eagle King be?)

2872
01:29:19,720 --> 01:29:20,520
Lord Tui said,

2873
01:29:20,520 --> 01:29:23,120
"This medicine was given
to me by that benefactor".

2874
01:29:23,120 --> 01:29:24,920
He got a secret medicine
from the benefactor.

2875
01:29:25,320 --> 01:29:28,040
It can make rotten ingredients
look fresh.

2876
01:29:28,100 --> 01:29:28,740
(Luckily, I got a secret medicine
from my benefactor)

2877
01:29:28,740 --> 01:29:29,380
(Who is the benefactor behind Lord Tui?)

2878
01:29:29,380 --> 01:29:30,100
(What medicine did they make?)

2879
01:29:30,120 --> 01:29:31,440
When you said all that, I kept thinking,

2880
01:29:31,440 --> 01:29:33,040
Golden Key. You got the Golden Key.

2881
01:29:33,040 --> 01:29:33,520
Right.

2882
01:29:33,520 --> 01:29:35,680
That was Lord Tui's Golden Key.

2883
01:29:35,680 --> 01:29:37,120
His benefactor gave it to him.

2884
01:29:37,120 --> 01:29:37,860
(That's a pretty fitting metaphor)

2885
01:29:39,640 --> 01:29:40,760
And then there's

2886
01:29:41,520 --> 01:29:42,320
your good friend,

2887
01:29:42,320 --> 01:29:43,680
Yan Reason.

2888
01:29:43,680 --> 01:29:44,920
We don't know where she is now.

2889
01:29:44,920 --> 01:29:45,940
(Where is Yan Reason now?)

2890
01:29:46,800 --> 01:29:48,040
You did win.

2891
01:29:48,040 --> 01:29:49,880
Your analysis was spot-on.

2892
01:29:50,800 --> 01:29:51,280
Everyone!

2893
01:29:52,480 --> 01:29:52,960
Everyone!

2894
01:29:55,760 --> 01:29:56,920
Jin,

2895
01:29:56,920 --> 01:29:58,160
you scared me to death.

2896
01:30:00,040 --> 01:30:00,720
Heroes,

2897
01:30:01,120 --> 01:30:03,600
Lord Tui's death has already
reached the imperial court.

2898
01:30:03,600 --> 01:30:05,440
Chancellor Tui is on his way here.

2899
01:30:06,520 --> 01:30:07,200
That serious?

2900
01:30:08,280 --> 01:30:09,240
After he arrives,

2901
01:30:09,240 --> 01:30:11,160
he'll take over all affairs in Tui City.

2902
01:30:11,160 --> 01:30:11,760
Chancellor Tui?

2903
01:30:12,520 --> 01:30:14,360
He's done for.

2904
01:30:17,280 --> 01:30:18,160
Whoever comes is dead.

2905
01:30:20,040 --> 01:30:21,520
Things are unstable now.

2906
01:30:21,520 --> 01:30:23,160
You heroes should lay low for a while.

2907
01:30:23,160 --> 01:30:24,120
Try not to move around too much.

2908
01:30:25,400 --> 01:30:25,640
Oh, right.

2909
01:30:26,360 --> 01:30:27,840
Someone told me

2910
01:30:27,840 --> 01:30:29,560
to hand this over

2911
01:30:29,560 --> 01:30:30,720
to whoever sits here.

2912
01:30:33,560 --> 01:30:34,280
That should be you, right?

2913
01:30:37,400 --> 01:30:38,480
Why would you say it's him?

2914
01:30:38,480 --> 01:30:40,600
He's the murderer.

2915
01:30:40,700 --> 01:30:41,880
(Not my place to judge the trial)
Farewell.

2916
01:30:41,880 --> 01:30:42,360
Alright.

2917
01:30:44,400 --> 01:30:46,400
How shameless.

2918
01:30:46,400 --> 01:30:47,080
Hold on.

2919
01:30:48,000 --> 01:30:49,320
Hold on again?

2920
01:30:49,320 --> 01:30:51,960
I killed a bad guy, friends!

2921
01:30:51,960 --> 01:30:54,240
Come on, didn't he deserve it?

2922
01:30:54,240 --> 01:30:56,440
And I paid off your debt, girl!

2923
01:30:56,440 --> 01:30:58,480
(Peacemaker Detective is online)
She's been blinded by Golden Keys.

2924
01:30:58,480 --> 01:30:59,880
(Survival instinct maxed out)
I saved your life.

2925
01:30:59,880 --> 01:31:00,800
You...

2926
01:31:00,800 --> 01:31:01,640
I mean, I...

2927
01:31:01,640 --> 01:31:02,480
I cured your poison.

2928
01:31:03,200 --> 01:31:05,040
(Aren't we on the same side?)
We killed him together.

2929
01:31:05,040 --> 01:31:06,280
Yes, I helped you.

2930
01:31:06,280 --> 01:31:07,840
But that's a separate matter.

2931
01:31:07,840 --> 01:31:08,960
You should thank me.

2932
01:31:08,960 --> 01:31:09,900
(Thank you, Ning)

2933
01:31:09,940 --> 01:31:10,770
(Big ingrate)

2934
01:31:10,770 --> 01:31:11,700
(Little ingrate)

2935
01:31:11,960 --> 01:31:12,800
Disciple,

2936
01:31:13,200 --> 01:31:15,520
a teacher for a day is a...

2937
01:31:15,520 --> 01:31:15,960
Father for life.

2938
01:31:16,020 --> 01:31:16,460
(Father)

2939
01:31:17,360 --> 01:31:18,040
(Father)
Got it?

2940
01:31:18,340 --> 01:31:19,020
(Father)

2941
01:31:19,020 --> 01:31:20,220
(Big Father)

2942
01:31:21,820 --> 01:31:23,100
(Today's emotional damage: billions)

2943
01:31:23,120 --> 01:31:24,680
And the kids in this city

2944
01:31:24,680 --> 01:31:25,280
should thank me too.

2945
01:31:25,640 --> 01:31:26,360
Right.

2946
01:31:26,360 --> 01:31:26,720
Exactly.

2947
01:31:26,720 --> 01:31:27,880
I don't remember it now,

2948
01:31:27,880 --> 01:31:29,400
but I'm happy to take the credit.

2949
01:31:30,840 --> 01:31:31,320
Why?

2950
01:31:31,320 --> 01:31:32,200
Because it says here,

2951
01:31:33,280 --> 01:31:34,360
thank you.

2952
01:31:34,360 --> 01:31:36,680
It's from the rescued kids of Tui City.

2953
01:31:38,360 --> 01:31:39,640
I tested poison for them.

2954
01:31:39,640 --> 01:31:40,480
Again and again.

2955
01:31:40,480 --> 01:31:41,400
Let's see what's in here.

2956
01:31:41,880 --> 01:31:44,000
I'll do it.

2957
01:31:44,000 --> 01:31:44,400
One piece.

2958
01:31:44,400 --> 01:31:45,220
(Brave Ding is growing up)

2959
01:31:46,880 --> 01:31:48,040
Stuffed bread!

2960
01:31:48,060 --> 01:31:49,380
(The hungry boy is online)

2961
01:31:51,800 --> 01:31:52,560
Cheers with buns.

2962
01:31:52,560 --> 01:31:55,840
Tomorrow, we'll solve
even more mysteries.

2963
01:31:55,840 --> 01:31:56,500
(Cheers with buns)
Okay.

2964
01:31:56,520 --> 01:31:57,480
Let's go.

2965
01:31:57,480 --> 01:31:59,240
Cheers.

2966
01:31:59,240 --> 01:32:00,720
Cheers!

2967
01:32:00,780 --> 01:32:02,460
(Detective eats first)

2968
01:32:04,580 --> 01:32:09,220
(With Chancellor Tui's arrival,
how will things unfold?)

2969
01:32:18,780 --> 01:32:20,700
(After this whole journey,
what do you feel and think?)

2970
01:32:20,720 --> 01:32:21,280
All these years,

2971
01:32:21,280 --> 01:32:23,120
Ning Waver was called

2972
01:32:23,120 --> 01:32:23,760
trash,

2973
01:32:23,760 --> 01:32:24,400
a lapdog,

2974
01:32:24,960 --> 01:32:26,800
but he never once

2975
01:32:26,800 --> 01:32:27,520
defended himself.

2976
01:32:27,880 --> 01:32:29,120
In the darkest corner,

2977
01:32:29,520 --> 01:32:30,400
he did the brightest thing.

2978
01:32:30,960 --> 01:32:32,560
The night has gone on too long.

2979
01:32:32,560 --> 01:32:34,880
It's time to use what's left
of me to light the way.

2980
01:32:35,120 --> 01:32:35,920
True courage

2981
01:32:35,920 --> 01:32:38,200
can mean being misunderstood
by the whole world

2982
01:32:38,200 --> 01:32:39,840
and still keeping the kindness
in your heart.

2983
01:32:39,840 --> 01:32:41,160
I hated Ning for so long.

2984
01:32:41,160 --> 01:32:42,120
In the end, I found out

2985
01:32:42,120 --> 01:32:43,000
he paid my debt

2986
01:32:43,000 --> 01:32:44,800
and kept me safe all along.

2987
01:32:44,800 --> 01:32:46,160
When rumors spread long enough,

2988
01:32:46,160 --> 01:32:47,330
people start calling them truth.

2989
01:32:47,560 --> 01:32:48,640
But time will prove

2990
01:32:48,640 --> 01:32:49,680
that those who stay true

2991
01:32:49,680 --> 01:32:51,240
don't need anyone's answer.

2992
01:32:51,240 --> 01:32:52,080
They are the answer.

2993
01:32:52,080 --> 01:32:55,160
I have to say this to that good man.

2994
01:32:55,160 --> 01:32:57,480
Ning,

2995
01:32:57,480 --> 01:32:58,160
I was wrong about you.

2996
01:32:58,160 --> 01:32:59,480
I always wanted to be a hero.

2997
01:32:59,480 --> 01:33:01,880
Then I found out Uncle Meng,
who taught me kung fu, was Ning.

2998
01:33:02,440 --> 01:33:03,760
Master!

2999
01:33:03,760 --> 01:33:05,520
A hero isn't the top fighter
on a ranking.

3000
01:33:05,520 --> 01:33:07,320
It's someone who teaches you kung fu

3001
01:33:07,320 --> 01:33:08,560
quietly in the night

3002
01:33:08,560 --> 01:33:09,880
and leaves without a word.

3003
01:33:09,880 --> 01:33:10,680
Fame fades.

3004
01:33:11,080 --> 01:33:13,280
But chivalry grows in people's hearts.

3005
01:33:13,280 --> 01:33:13,960
I

3006
01:33:13,960 --> 01:33:14,880
hated him deeply,

3007
01:33:15,120 --> 01:33:16,120
but I respected him too.

3008
01:33:16,320 --> 01:33:17,920
After I learned he was undercover,

3009
01:33:17,920 --> 01:33:20,120
I realized he'd carried too much alone.

3010
01:33:20,480 --> 01:33:21,600
So on his final road,

3011
01:33:21,600 --> 01:33:22,240
I'll walk with him.

3012
01:33:22,920 --> 01:33:23,680
True righteousness

3013
01:33:24,200 --> 01:33:25,840
isn't being worshiped from above.

3014
01:33:26,600 --> 01:33:27,800
It's kneeling in the mud

3015
01:33:27,800 --> 01:33:29,320
and still being willing

3016
01:33:29,320 --> 01:33:30,080
to light a lamp for this city.

3017
01:33:30,080 --> 01:33:32,240
When I cursed him with a straw doll,

3018
01:33:32,240 --> 01:33:32,680
I didn't know

3019
01:33:32,680 --> 01:33:34,880
he was the one risking his life
to test medicine for the kids.

3020
01:33:35,440 --> 01:33:37,000
These kids are Tui Kingdom's future.

3021
01:33:37,640 --> 01:33:38,520
If my life

3022
01:33:38,520 --> 01:33:39,600
can keep them alive,

3023
01:33:39,920 --> 01:33:40,680
it's worth it.

3024
01:33:40,680 --> 01:33:42,040
Don't be so quick to hate someone.

3025
01:33:42,040 --> 01:33:42,960
The truth may be late,

3026
01:33:43,440 --> 01:33:44,400
but it'll show up.

3027
01:33:44,400 --> 01:33:46,560
On behalf of the people
in the city, thank you.

3028
01:33:46,560 --> 01:33:48,360
